headline: Becton, Dickinson Shareholders Approve All Proposals at Annual Meeting, Recap Record FY2025
summary: Becton, Dickinson and Company (NYSE:BDX) shareholders approved all four proposals presented at the company’s annual meeting, including the election of directors and an amendment to the company’s equity compensation plan, according to preliminary voting results shared during the event.
